_sText:
Previous version was Breaker_Beta2. 
Differences: The 'secret' area now has water to prevent you from dying when falling from above, and to make it more obvious that someone is in the secret area. The tiles that need to be broken to get to above mentioned area is now much more obvious, seen in Screen shot 3 as the newer looking concrete. Re-textured everything but the main walls, and the breakable blocks. The "shield" at the base of spawn can now be shot through, this IS intentional. That's about it.
Have Fun
